<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المَفْعُولِ بِهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> الِاسْمُ المَنْصُوبُ الَّذِي يَقَعُ عَلَيْهِ الفِعْلُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> ضَرَبْتُ زَيْداً، وَرَكِبْتُ الفَرَسَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ قِسْمَانِ:</span> ظَاهِرٌ، وَمُضْمَرٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَالظَّاهِرُ؛ مَا تَقَدَّمَ ذِكْرُهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالمُضْمَرُ قِسْمَانِ:</span> مُتَّصِلٌ، وَمُنْفَصِلٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَالمُتَّصِلُ اثْنَا عَشَرَ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> ضَرَبَنِي، وَضَرَبَنَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَضَرَبَكَ، وَضَرَبَكِ، وَضَرَبَكُمَا، وَضَرَبَكُمْ، وَضَرَبَكُنَّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>